	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam et pacem a domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person132">Lavaterus</persName>, vir optimus, in senatum allectus est<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Zur Wahl <persName ref="person132">Hans Rudolf Lavaters</persName> in den Kleinen Rat s. <hi>Stucki</hi> 153-155.</note>.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Idem vero religioni et iustitiae publicę favet egregie.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Deinde vir est magnanimus, opulentus, fortis, constans et eloquens; unde boni viii non mediocriter laetantur ob vocationem eius.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu hoc consuli<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Gemeint ist wahrscheinlich Jakob <persName ref="person1641">Meyer</persName> (vgl. <hi>Stucki</hi> 154f; amtierender Bürgermeister war zu diesem Zeitpunkt allerdings Adelberg <persName ref="person1641">Meyer</persName>.</note> significabis, orabitisque dominum, ut dona sua in eo homine augeat et confirmet.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ad ea, quae scripsisti de Valesiis<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Oben <ref target="file10881">Nr. 842</ref>, 28-40.</note>, obstupui, quanquam ab initio perfidiam et imposturam timui.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque <placeName ref="place121">Bernates</placeName> ab istis nunc deserti sunt, quibus tamen, ut audio, confisi sunt plurimum<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Vgl. oben <ref target="file10782">Nr. 744</ref>, 63-82; 750, 12-15; 752, 35f.</note>.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ita propediem damnum a Gallo<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">König <persName ref="person859">Franz I.</persName></note> accipient maximum.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunquam enim impiorum societas bonis bene cessit<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Vgl. oben <ref target="file10880">Nr. 841</ref>, 27f.</note>.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Et nos quotidie experimur, quid nobis impia incomodent foedera.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De conventu<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Vgl. oben <ref target="file10881">Nr. 842</ref>, 17-25.</note> ne verbum quidem habeo.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid sperare debeam, nescio.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc certum autem apud me est, veritatem perpetuo superaturam.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Neque ego tanti fecero istorum conscriptionem, si veritati repugnans statuerint.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Igitur pacato apud me sum animo, quod istud attinet negotium.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interim doleo propter quorundam impudentiam et male feriata negotia.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es wirt der kampff wären biß inn das end.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cribrabimur<note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8">Vgl. Lk 22,31.</note>, per ignem explorabit nos dominus<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9">Vgl. Sach 13,9.</note>.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Beati, qui perseverant in finem usque<note xml:id="fn10" type="footnote" n="10">Vgl. Mt 10, 22; 24, 13.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De bello si quid habes, scribe.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person226">Vadianus</persName> a Sangallo scribit<note xml:id="fn11" type="footnote" n="11"><persName ref="person226">Vadians</persName> Brief ist nicht erhalten.</note> Turcam certo equitatu magno ingressum Hungariam, aciem dirigere in <placeName ref="place35">Austriam</placeName><note xml:id="fn12" type="footnote" n="12">Zum Gerücht über einen gegen <placeName ref="place32">Ungarn</placeName> gerichteten Angriffsplan des Sultans <persName ref="person2269">Suleiman I.</persName> und zu den Übergriffen des Paschas von <placeName ref="place105">Belgrad</placeName>, die besonders <placeName ref="place82">Slawonien</placeName> betrafen, vgl. Erasmus, Corr. XI 325, 34; Nuntiaturberichte aus Deutschland 1533-1559, Bd. I, Nuntiaturen des Vergerio 1533-1536, bearb. v. Walter Friedensburg, Gotha 1892, S. 574,29-575,4.</note>.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec videlicet illa christiani regis consilia sunt<note xml:id="fn13" type="footnote" n="13">Zu Bullingers Kritik an der Türkenpolitik König Franz' I. vgl. oben <ref target="file10880">Nr. 841</ref>, 23.</note>.</s>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid vero multis opus?</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domini gladius Imminet cervicibus nostris.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus misereatur nostri.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Venit ad vos Frisius<note xml:id="fn14" type="footnote" n="14"><persName ref="person69">Johannes Fries</persName>.</note> noster nobis longe charissimus.</s>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hunc nos<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">nos <hi>über gestrichenem</hi> ego.</note> tibi et <persName ref="person81">Gryneo</persName> ceu fidelissimis patribus charissimum Commendamus filium.</s>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Obsecramus vos, ut hunc ceu viscera nostra complectamini.</s>
					<s n="29" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vir est doctus, Pius et probus.</s>
					<s n="30" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quicquid offitii in hunc contuleritis, in hominem dignissimum contuleritis, et nos, quantum in nobis est, vestris respondebimus benefitiis.</s>
					<s n="31" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Acceptum ergo duces ad <persName ref="person81">Grynaeum</persName> oreque proprio hunc commendabis et literis hisce nostris.</s>
					<s n="32" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Id, dum vivam, agnoscam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="33" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><pb type="edition" next="330"/>Vale, <persName ref="person154">Myconi</persName>, amicorum charissime, et frequentius scribe.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="34" xml:lang="la" type="auto">12. iunii 1536.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="35" xml:lang="la" type="auto">H. Bullingerus tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="36" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro d. <persName ref="person154">Osvaldo Myconio</persName>, celeberrimae urbis <placeName ref="place97">Basileae</placeName> episcopo, suo in domino charissimo fratri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
